  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring Back The Sun</h2><br>Bring Back The Sun is a simple but challenging 2D Platformer. <br>The focus is on jumping right and only that. No enemies, no spikes, no wall jumps, no double jumps. Just simple jumps to get through the levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A pure experience<br></li><li> Challenging but not hardcore<br></li><li> Jump through <strong>over 40 levels</strong><br></li><li> Minimalistic graphics<br></li><li> <strong>Full Controller Support</strong><br></li><li> Atmospheric soundtrack</li></ul><br>You can expect 1-3 hours playtime for your first run depending on your skill level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437210/extras/eec6a07145715946ade336cb9037314f.poster.avif?t=1727827171\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437210/extras/eec6a07145715946ade336cb9037314f.webm?t=1727827171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437210/extras/eec6a07145715946ade336cb9037314f.mp4?t=1727827171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
